    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さとみによるユニットの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡA few days after the members of the unit",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "メンバーが決まって数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "were chosen by Satomi",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "私って子供っぽいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it true that I look like a kid?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりどうしたんだ？　何か言われたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's all this about all of a sudden? Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3333332856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃないんですけど……今回のユニットは\n各グループの最年少が集まってますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not that‚ but… In this unit‚\nthe youngest members from each group are gathered‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルのすみれちゃん、リズノワのこころちゃん\n月ストのすずちゃん、サニピの雫ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's Sumire-chan from TRINITYAiLE‚ Kokoro-chan from LizNoir‚\nSuzu-chan from Moon Tempest‚ and Shizuku-chan from Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな年少組のユニットに\nどうして私が選ばれたのかなって思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wondered why I was chosen for a unit\nwith such young members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "年齢なら、琴乃ちゃんや瑠依さん、葵さんも\n私と同い年ですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In terms of age‚ Kotono-chan‚ Rui-san‚ and\nAoi-san are the same age as me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "私より年下の優ちゃんや芽衣ちゃんもいるのに\nみんなを差し置いて年少組に交じるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even Yu-chan and Mei-chan‚ who are younger than me‚ are there…\nI can't believe I joined the younger group without everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "私ってそんなに子供っぽく見えるんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I look that childish?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.566666619,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}